626
00:37:32.270 --> 00:37:36.180
associated with progenitors, and suppression of

627
00:37:36.260 --> 00:37:37.740
Myc target gene sets.

628
00:37:44.760 --> 00:37:46.800
So AMX883

629
00:37:48.240 --> 00:37:51.720
induces rapid and prolonged degradation of

630
00:37:51.740 --> 00:37:55.320
BRD9. On the left-hand side, we have a subcut tumor,

631
00:37:55.900 --> 00:37:59.820
MV411-derived tumor, and you can see prolonged

632
00:37:59.980 --> 00:38:03.900
degradation of the target, and that does outlast the pharmacokinetics of the

633
00:38:03.960 --> 00:38:04.500
compound.

634
00:38:05.720 --> 00:38:09.680
On the right-hand side, using a disseminated model

635
00:38:09.720 --> 00:38:13.560
of MV411, using flow cytometry measure, we can

636
00:38:13.640 --> 00:38:17.260
measure in the bone marrow, you can see induction of two markers of

