00:38:39.860 --> 00:38:43.740
and schedules of AMX883, venetoclax, or vehicle.

643
00:38:44.250 --> 00:38:48.220
And you can see during the dosing period, we didn't lose any of the

644
00:38:48.300 --> 00:38:52.220
animals treated with AMX883, whereas all of the animals

