00:45:44.616 --> 00:45:48.316
do you see an effect on the normal healthy PBMCs for

769
00:45:48.356 --> 00:45:52.006
your BRD9 degradation? Does that induce immunosuppression in your mouse

770
00:45:52.076 --> 00:45:53.536
models?

771
00:45:54.156 --> 00:45:56.706
We don't have great cross-reactivity

772
00:45:57.356 --> 00:45:59.236
with

773
00:46:00.036 --> 00:46:03.736
the mouse, so I'm not sure we'd see it there.

774
00:46:03.776 --> 00:46:07.356
But we've completed tox studies on this, and that is not something we've

775
00:46:07.836 --> 00:46:11.716
seen in higher animals as well. It's a

