00:46:38.376 --> 00:46:38.516
Yeah.

786
00:46:38.656 --> 00:46:42.536
Can you comment on if you've looked at heart PD,

787
00:46:43.536 --> 00:46:47.356
BRD9 degradation in the heart, and also your expectations for safety?

788
00:46:48.976 --> 00:46:52.956
Yeah. So I think you probably are alluding to

789
00:46:53.016 --> 00:46:56.556
some observations. So for context here, two PROTACs,

