00:47:20.080 --> 00:47:21.460
this. So we've gone above and beyond.

798
00:47:21.500 --> 00:47:25.200
We've done work in human cardiac myocytes, we've done work

799
00:47:25.700 --> 00:47:28.880
in telemetered animals in vivo to understand.

800
00:47:28.920 --> 00:47:32.500
And we can't see, at least pre-clinically, we cannot see

